<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>New Design Quote Request</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>A user has requested quote(s) for one or more designs. The details of
      their submitted request are below.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>First Name: {{firstName}}</li>
      <li>Last Name: {{lastName}}</li>
      <li>Email: {{email}}</li>
      <li>Phone number: {{phone}}</li>
      <li>Union: {{union}}</li>
      <li>Comments: {{comments}}</li>

      <table style="border-collapse: collapse;">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th
              style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 8px; background-color: lightgray;"
            >Design Number</th>
            <th
              style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 8px; background-color: lightgray;"
            >Garment Color</th>
            <th
              style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 8px; background-color: lightgray;"
            >Link To Design</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {{#each designs}}
            <tr>
              <td
                style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 8px;"
              >{{designNumber}}</td>
              <td
                style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 8px;"
              >{{garmentColor}}</td>
              <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 8px;"><a
                  href="https://www.imagepointe.com/design-library/?viewDesign={{id}}"
                >View Design</a></td>
            </tr>
          {{/each}}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </ul>
  </body>
</html>